text: Tobias Alistair P. "Toby" Kebbell (born 9 July 1982) is an English actor. He is known for his roles in the movies Dead Man's Shoes, Prince of Persia: The Sands of Time, The Sorcerer's Apprentice, War Horse, Wrath of the Titans and Kong: Skull Island. Kebbell won the Best Supporting Actor Award at the British Independent Film Awards"The British Independent Film Awards" for Control. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1982 births Category:English movie actors Category:Living people
